  }, "The Film Community"), mdx("p", null, "I think the most obvious piece of advice that you\u2019ll hear about any hobby is, find a community! I follow a lot of directors, film societies, entertainment writers, and amateur and professional film critics on Twitter and an app called Letterboxd. Letterboxd is the app I use to record what films I watch, keep a watchlist of films I want to watch, and read reviews and lists. Think of it as Goodreads for movies, though I personally think Letterboxd\u2019s UI is way better. I love the app a lot. ", mdx("a", {
